            <item>
                <title>This is way more elegant than I could ever put it</title>
                <dc:creator></dc:creator>
                
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The data may not contain the answer. The combination of some data and an aching desire for an answer does not ensure that a reasonable answer can be extracted from a given body of data.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;-John Tukey &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.johndcook.com/blog/2009/02/18/the-data-may-not-contain-the-answer/&quot;&gt;from my favorite stats blog&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
                
